title: Wood vertical file

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a wood vertical file, as shown and described.

description: My new design for a wood vertical file can be in an oak and/or a cherry wood finish for use with a four-drawer vertical file, a two-drawer vertical file, and a two-drawer lateral file.
